.SH NAME
audit_signal_info_syscall \- record signal info for syscalls
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" audit_signal_info_syscall
.BI "(struct task_struct *t "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "t" 12
task being signaled
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
If the audit subsystem is being terminated, record the task (pid)
and uid that is doing that.
